1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 14=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=Marry Me, Will You?=

4
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:59,350
(She seems to have lost
all her memories.)

5
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:01,150
(Perhaps that's for the best.)

6
00:01:04,120 --> 00:01:05,230
You can't kill me.

7
00:01:05,241 --> 00:01:07,006
So, you plan to torture me
to death instead?

8
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,680
Stop pretending.

9
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:11,070
When you were hurt before,

10
00:01:11,533 --> 00:01:13,000
didn't you say you couldn't feel pain?

11
00:01:14,269 --> 00:01:15,363
The medicine's been applied.

12
00:01:15,510 --> 00:01:16,430
Can I leave now?

13
00:01:22,350 --> 00:01:23,310
When you choose a man,

14
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:25,400
keep your eyes wide open.

15
00:01:26,063 --> 00:01:27,870
Pick someone who'll guard you
with his heart.

16
00:01:27,870 --> 00:01:29,200
The one I chose is Che.

17
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:31,400
He's the right one for me.

18
00:01:35,150 --> 00:01:37,150
What a devoted couple.

19
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:39,280
I wish you a blissful union.

20
00:01:41,350 --> 00:01:42,430
Such an act.

21
00:01:47,710 --> 00:01:49,760
You haven't changed at all.

22
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,400
Che.

23
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,400
Zhaoli.

24
00:02:13,650 --> 00:02:15,177
Did the ruler make things hard for you?

25
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,680
Is it because of me?

26
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,080
Of course not.

27
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,360
Don't worry.

28
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,430
I'll make sure you're safe.

29
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:25,840
Let's go home.

30
00:02:29,590 --> 00:02:30,430
Alright.

31
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,640
Your Majesty,

32
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,120
as you ordered,

33
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:53,520
we've set tight surveillance on Yan Che.

34
00:02:54,750 --> 00:02:56,000
If he shows any sign of trouble,

35
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,910
protect Zhaoli at once.

36
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,240
Understood.

37
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,540
However,

38
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,400
Your Majesty,

39
00:03:02,710 --> 00:03:04,360
since you have doubts,

40
00:03:04,403 --> 00:03:06,120
wouldn't it be simpler
to end him outright?

41
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,193
Why keep investigating him?

42
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,080
Who are you?

43
00:03:13,206 --> 00:03:14,240
How do you know my spells?

44
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,030
Zhaoli, it's dangerous!

45
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,710
It was you who used Ye Li

46
00:03:17,721 --> 00:03:19,146
to strike against Zhaoli, wasn't it?

47
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,080
Right.

48
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:23,240
I'll rid her of this threat.

49
00:03:28,310 --> 00:03:29,150
Your Majesty,

50
00:03:29,161 --> 00:03:30,349
your health has just improved.

51
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,710
Please, take care of yourself.

52
00:03:34,030 --> 00:03:35,150
Convey my decree.

53
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:36,203
Tomorrow, no one is allowed

54
00:03:36,310 --> 00:03:37,590
to attend the wedding feast.

55
00:03:37,590 --> 00:03:38,430
Yes.

56
00:03:41,150 --> 00:03:41,990
Zhaoli,

57
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:44,960
the ruler is acting
increasingly recklessly.

58
00:03:45,549 --> 00:03:46,470
It must be hard on you.

59
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:47,590
Che,

60
00:03:48,116 --> 00:03:50,120
why does the ruler hold
such hostility toward you?

61
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,960
He's always believed

62
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:56,190
I bear ill intent toward the tribe.

63
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,360
But as you know,

64
00:04:00,030 --> 00:04:01,310
the tribe is my home.

65
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:02,560
How could I ever...

66
00:04:03,986 --> 00:04:04,826
Forget it.

67
00:04:04,857 --> 00:04:06,526
If you don't wish
to be dragged into this,

68
00:04:06,537 --> 00:04:07,960
I'll call off the wedding tomorrow.

69
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:15,800
Che.

70
00:04:25,430 --> 00:04:26,800
Tomorrow, our wedding

71
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,950
will go on as planned.

72
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,120
(If I marry Che,)

73
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,070
(perhaps everything will change,)

74
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,600
(and everyone can live in peace.)

75
00:04:41,860 --> 00:04:44,140
(Auspicious Elegance, Joy)

76
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,520
Che,

77
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:05,000
as Grandmother said,

78
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,070
we must first drink the nuptial wine

79
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,430
before you can lift the veil.

80
00:05:26,590 --> 00:05:27,800
You've drunk the nuptial wine.

81
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:29,870
I am your husband now.

82
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,510
No backing out, alright?

83
00:05:39,210 --> 00:05:40,070
I just said that.

84
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:41,310
And now you want to back out?

85
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,130
Ying Du,

86
00:05:43,190 --> 00:05:44,630
today is my wedding day.

87
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,510
What exactly are you after?

88
00:05:46,610 --> 00:05:47,490
Wrong.

89
00:05:47,510 --> 00:05:48,870
It's our

90
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:50,240
wedding day.

91
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,200
You...

92
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:52,880
Zhaoli.

93
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,560
Che.

94
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:03,240
I won't let you harm him.

95
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:05,190
Beg again,

96
00:06:05,430 --> 00:06:06,510
and I'll kill him.

97
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:07,400
Zhaoli.

98
00:06:07,430 --> 00:06:08,270
You...

99
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:10,240
Put me down.

100
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,400
Let me go.

101
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:19,110
No!

102
00:06:19,110 --> 00:06:20,000
Che!

103
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:22,350
Let me go.

104
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,270
Release Zhaoli.

105
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,800
You truly have no fear of death.

106
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,870
Why do you always target me?

107
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:31,040
And now, you wish to take my wife away,

108
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,310
defying moral codes.

109
00:06:32,390 --> 00:06:33,750
A disgrace to the Wuyue tribe.

110
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,000
It is not your place to question me.

111
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,000
No matter what,

112
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,480
she will never belong to you.

113
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:47,720
I forbid you from hurting Che.

114
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,720
You shield him that much?

115
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,520
Yes.

116
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,720
One day, you'll see his true nature.

117
00:07:06,630 --> 00:07:08,310
Let go. Let me go!

118
00:07:11,190 --> 00:07:12,030
Zhaoli.

119
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:14,360
Marry me,

120
00:07:15,430 --> 00:07:16,270
will you?

121
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:23,270
Do you even know what you're saying?

122
00:07:24,630 --> 00:07:26,600
I'm already Che's wife now.

123
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,870
On the wedding night,

124
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:31,270
I shared the nuptial wine with you.

125
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,480
How could you claim to be his wife?

126
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:35,480
What exactly are you trying to do?

127
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,360
I truly don't understand.

128
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:40,160
Why are you trapping me here?

129
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:42,920
What did I do wrong

130
00:07:43,190 --> 00:07:44,680
that made you treat me this way?

131
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,390
No matter where you go,

132
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:50,600
there's nowhere safer than by my side.

133
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:57,790
That's right.

134
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,800
Instead of staying elsewhere,

135
00:08:01,270 --> 00:08:03,190
spending each day plotting to kill you,

136
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:06,120
I might as well stay by your side,

137
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,560
waiting for the right chance

138
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,560
to strike a single fatal blow.

139
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,000
Fine.

140
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,070
Just stay by my side,

141
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,360
and you can do anything you want.

142
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,440
Zhaoli,

143
00:08:23,016 --> 00:08:24,253
something's wrong with Yan Che.

144
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,430
You must not marry him.

145
00:08:27,070 --> 00:08:27,910
Zhaoli.

146
00:08:29,490 --> 00:08:30,390
Ying Du,

147
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:31,360
shame on you.

148
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,440
How could you drug me?

149
00:08:38,290 --> 00:08:42,940
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

150
00:08:44,770 --> 00:08:49,740
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

151
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:54,480
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

152
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:57,380
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

153
00:08:57,900 --> 00:09:03,190
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

154
00:09:03,190 --> 00:09:06,890
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

155
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:09,590
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

156
00:09:09,590 --> 00:09:13,630
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

157
00:09:13,630 --> 00:09:16,010
♪And that is enough♪

158
00:09:16,010 --> 00:09:19,800
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

159
00:09:20,010 --> 00:09:22,770
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

160
00:09:23,140 --> 00:09:28,890
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

